title: iCMV-Vector - 1
treatment_protocol_ch1: To induce TRF2dMdB, both cell lines were treated with 1uG/ml of doxycyline
growth_protocol_ch1: Inducible CMV-Vector and CMV-TRF2dBdM were grown in DMEM aupplemented with 10%  tetracycline free FBS. Media was changed at day 4
extract_protocol_ch1: RNA was extracted using Qiagen RNeasy Mini kit, using Qiashredder for lysate homogenization.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared from 500 ng total RNA according to theThe Ambion iii ® WT Expression Kit Protocol For Affymetrix® GeneChip® Whole Transcript (WT) Expression Arrays protocol in conjunction with the Affymetrix® GeneChip® WT Terminal Labeling Kit.
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 17 hr at 45C on Human Gene 1.0 ST arrays. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix GeneChip® Fluidics Station 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the GeneChip® Scanner 3000 7G.
data_processing: Microarray data processing and analysis was carried out at EMBL. All analyses were carried out in R (v.2.13.0). Microarray data were normalized using Robust Multichip Average (RMA) and differentially expressed genes were identified using Linear Models for MicroArrays (LIMMA). A cut-off of a Benjamini-Hochberg false discovery rate (BH) <0.05 was used to identify significant genes.
contact_institute: MRC London Institute of Medical Sciences
contact_address: Hammersmith Hospital Campus, Du Cane Road
